author: Cleo Abram
description:
This mantis Shrimp can punch faster than the blink of an eye with a force about 100x its own body weight. That’s the strongest self-powered punch in the animal kingdom! 

Their little fists of fury, known as dactyl clubs, are uniquely designed to absorb the shockwaves of their own creation… and engineers have taken note…

For more optimistic science and tech stories, subscribe!

title: What Animal Has The Fastest Punch?
